ck, Michael Patrick, Aileen, Brigid, Paddy, Siobhan, John Patrick, Kevin Patrick, Parnell.","Irish (Cork and Kerry): shortened form of   O'Sullivan  ."],"variants":[{"name":"O'Sullivan","meanings":["Some characteristic forenames:  Irish Brendan, Donal, Liam, Siobhan, Declan, Kieran, Cathal, Dermot, Eamon, Fergus, Grainne, Seamus.","Irish (Munster): Anglicized form of Gaelic <b>Ó Súileabháin</b> ‘descendant of <i>Súileabhán</i>’, a personal name from <i>súil</i> ‘eye’ + <i>dubh</i> ‘dark’ + the diminutive suffix <i>-án</i>. Compare   Sullivan  ."]},{"name":"Sullivant","meanings":["Irish: variant of   Sullivan  ."]}]}],"lifeSummary":"When Anne Sullivan was born about 1130, in Berwick, Dorset, England, her father, Alexander Sullivan, was 32 and her mother, Mrs. Alexander Sullivan, was 27. She had at least 1 son with Sir Robert de Russell II. She died on 17 June 1185, at the age of 56."},"et":{"about 1130–June 17 1185":"umbes 1130–17. juuni 1185","1130–1185":"1130–1185","1125–1201":"1125–1201","1150–1230":"1150–1230","1100–Male":"1100–Surnud","1105–Female":"1105–Surnud","about 1150":"umbes 1150","June 17 1185":"17. juuni 1185","1105":"1105","1125":"1125","1201":"1201","1100":"1100","1230":"1230","1185":"1185","1130":"1130","1150":"1150","about 1130":"umbes 1130","Berwick, Dorset, England":"Berwick, Dorset, England"},"fi":{"about 1130–June 17 1185":"noin 1130–17. kesäkuuta 1185","1130–1185":"1130–1185","1125–1201":"1125–1201","1150–1230":"1150–1230","1100–Male":"1100–Kuollut","1105–Female":"1105–Kuollut","about 1150":"noin 1150","June 17 1185":"17. kesäkuuta 1185","1105":"1105","1125":"1125","1201":"1201","1100":"1100","1230":"1230","1185":"1185","1130":"1130","1150":"1150","about 1130":"noin 1130","Berwick, Dorset, England":"Berwick, Dorset, England"},"fr":{"about 1130–June 17 1185":"environ 1130–17 juin 1185","1130–1185":"1130–1185","1125–1201":"1125–1201","1150–1230":"1150–1230","1100–Male":"1100–Décédé","1105–Female":"1105–Décédée","about 1150":"environ 1150","June 1